item.title: CVE-2021-21622|2024-08-03T18:16:23.681Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20artifact%20repository%20parameter%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Artifact Repository Parameter Plugin 1.0.0 and earlier does not escape parameter names and descriptions, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Job/Configure permission.
